                        an attitude.)<br /><br /><span style="font-weight: bold;">Zoak </span>(p. 357): Some changes to this beastie which didn't
                        make it into the PDF. S/be: <span style="font-weight: bold;">STR</span>: 5; Claws (3): 8; <span style="font-weight: bold;">Knockdown</span>:
                        5; <span style="font-weight: bold;">Legend Points</span>: 70
                        
